{"type": "article", "id": 10347, "title": "New Old Divider 屏风", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-03T08:32:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142312p1GcCzsYR28Bnjlv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Kimu Lab 是一家来自台湾的设计工作室，他们推出了一个叫做 “New Old Divider” 的屏风产品，把中国传统元素和西式设计结合在一起，框架采用现代化的铝合金，而屏风的构成则采用了传统的纸扇面。纸扇可以自由展开或收起，既可以承担屏风的功能，满足不同的功能需求，装饰意味又强烈。这是<a href=\"http://www.kimulab.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计工作室的官方主页</a>，可以查看他们更多作品。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142309IVwBnqLX79lkF1xt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142310hRwUC2acrbWulDBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142310cAfepPDCHasTKqB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142310dE4VbcMHOfm8ejUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142311c8JPpvwFSrV1HqO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}